== Besondere Auszeichnungen ==
{| class="wikitable" width="100%"
|-
|rowspan="2" width="20%"|'''[[Ehrenoscar]]'''
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[The March of Time]]
|-
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[W. Howard Greene]] und [[Harold Rosson]]
|-
|width="20%"|'''[[Oscar/Academy Award of Merit|Academy Award of Merit]]'''
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[Douglas Shearer]] und [[Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer|M-G-M SSD]] for the development of a practical two-way horn system and a biased Class A push-pull recording system
|-
|rowspan="2" width="20%"|'''[[Oscar/Wissenschaft und Entwicklung|Preis für Wissenschaft und Entwicklung]]'''
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[Edward C. Wente]] und [[Bell Telephone Laboratories]] for their multi-cellular high-frequency horn and receiver
|-
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[RCA Records|RCA-Victor]] for their rotary stabilizer sound head
|-
|rowspan="4" width="20%"|'''[[Oscar/Technische Verdienste|Preis für Technische Verdienste]]'''
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[RCA Records|RCA-Victor]] for their development of a method of recording and printing sound records utilizing a restricted spectrum (known as ultra-violet light recording)
|-
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[Altec Lansing|Electrical Research Products Inc.]] for the ERPI 'Type Q' portable recording channel
|-
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[RCA Records|RCA-Victor]] for furnishing a practical design and specifications for a non-slip printer
|-
|width="80%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"|[[United Artists]] Studio Corp. for the development of a practical, efficient and quiet wind machine
|}

